Package com.latencybusters.lbmct

Provides "Connected Topics" semantics for Ultra Messaging.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    LbmCtRcvConnCreateCallback
    Callback interface to deliver the "connection created" event to a receiving application.
    LbmCtRcvConnDeleteCallback
    Callback interface to deliver the "connection deleted" event to a receiving application.
    LbmCtSrcConnCreateCallback
    Callback interface to deliver the "connection created" event to a source application.
    LbmCtSrcConnDeleteCallback
    Callback interface to deliver the "connection deleted" event to a source application.
    TmrCallback
    Interface for timer callbacks associated with Tmr.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    LbmCt
    An instance of the Connected Topics for Ultra Messaging (UM).
    LbmCtConfig
    Container object holding configuration of an instance of LbmCt.
    LbmCtPeerInfo
    A passive object that provides useful information to a Connected Topics application.
    LbmCtRcv
    A connected receiver.
    LbmCtRcvConn
    Connection object, mostly for internal use by CT.
    LbmCtSrc
    A connected source.

Package com.latencybusters.lbmct Description

Provides "Connected Topics" semantics for Ultra Messaging. See https://github.com/UltraMessaging/lbmct for overview and user manual.
